image_analysis.description: This is a single page from a financial disclosure form, identified as OGE Form 278e. The document lists various business entities, their ownership structure, and related individuals or trusts. The filer's name is identified as Donald J. Trump. The page number is A14 of 47.
image_analysis.layout: The document has a structured, tabular layout. A header contains the form number, filer's name, and page number. The main body consists of numbered entries (156 through 167), each detailing a business entity. For each entity, information about ownership percentages, owning parties, and their roles is provided. A footer contains a document identifier.
